==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Structureless
<hw>Struc"ture*less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without a
definite structure, or arrangement of parts; without organization;
devoid of cells; homogeneous; <as>as, a <ex>structureless</ex>
membrane</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Structurist</ent>⟦br⟧
